TimeROC Dataset Summary Information

Source: R/data_timeroc_docs.R
timeroc_datasets_summary.Rd

Summary table providing overview of all TimeROC test datasets including sample sizes, descriptions, key features, and recommended analysis parameters.

Usage

timeroc_datasets_summary

Format

A data frame with 6 observations and 6 variables:

Dataset

Character. Dataset name

Observations

Integer. Number of observations

Description

Character. Brief dataset description

Key_Features

Character. Main features and characteristics

Primary_Endpoint

Character. Recommended primary endpoint variable

Biomarker_Variable

Character. Recommended biomarker variable(s)

Source

Generated by create_timeroc_test_data.R

Details

This summary table provides a quick reference for all TimeROC test datasets, helping users select appropriate datasets for their testing needs and understand the key characteristics of each dataset.
